'''Oke osimiri''' bu miri ukwu-ukwu na ba uwa buru-buru. Adi otu oke osimiri n'uwa, nke ana kpo ''World Ocean'', a kewasi ya n'ise: [[Pacific Ocean|Pacific]], [[Atlantic Ocean|Atlantic]], ma ufodi, [[Indian Ocean|Indian]], [[Arctic Ocean|Arctic]], na [[Southern Ocean|Southern]].

''Pacific Ocean'' bu miri hiri nne, kachasiri osimiri ndi ozo, ''Atlantic Ocean'' a soro ya.

